HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES, September 29, 2025.
The committee on Financial Services, to whom was referred the
petition (accompanied by bill, House, No. 1223) of Sally P. Kerans and
Kristin E. Kassner relative to providing health insurance coverage for
scalp and facial hair prosthesis, reports recommending that the
accompanying bill (House, No. 4552) ought to pass.
For the committee,
JAMES M. MURPHY.

